4713 /******************** USART Instances : Synchronous mode **********************/
4714 #define IS_USART_INSTANCE(INSTANCE) (((INSTANCE) == USART1) || \
4715  ((INSTANCE) == USART2) || \
4716  ((INSTANCE) == USART6))
4717 
4718 /******************** UART Instances : Asynchronous mode **********************/
4719 #define IS_UART_INSTANCE(INSTANCE) (((INSTANCE) == USART1) || \
4720  ((INSTANCE) == USART2) || \
4721  ((INSTANCE) == USART6))
4722 
4723 /****************** UART Instances : Hardware Flow control ********************/
4724 #define IS_UART_HWFLOW_INSTANCE(INSTANCE) (((INSTANCE) == USART1) || \
4725  ((INSTANCE) == USART2) || \
4726  ((INSTANCE) == USART6))
4727 
4728 /********************* UART Instances : Smard card mode ***********************/
4729 #define IS_SMARTCARD_INSTANCE(INSTANCE) (((INSTANCE) == USART1) || \
4730  ((INSTANCE) == USART2) || \
4731  ((INSTANCE) == USART6))
4732 
4733 /*********************** UART Instances : IRDA mode ***************************/
4734 #define IS_IRDA_INSTANCE(INSTANCE) (((INSTANCE) == USART1) || \
4735  ((INSTANCE) == USART2) || \
4736  ((INSTANCE) == USART6))
4737 
4738 /****************************** IWDG Instances ********************************/
4739 #define IS_IWDG_ALL_INSTANCE(INSTANCE) ((INSTANCE) == IWDG)
4740 
4741 /****************************** WWDG Instances ********************************/
4742 #define IS_WWDG_ALL_INSTANCE(INSTANCE) ((INSTANCE) == WWDG)
4743 
4744 /****************************** SDIO Instances ********************************/
4745 #define IS_SDIO_ALL_INSTANCE(INSTANCE) ((INSTANCE) == SDIO)
4746

4748 #define USB_OTG_FS_HOST_MAX_CHANNEL_NBR 8
4749 #define USB_OTG_FS_MAX_IN_ENDPOINTS 4 /* Including EP0 */
4750 #define USB_OTG_FS_MAX_OUT_ENDPOINTS 4 /* Including EP0 */
4751 #define USB_OTG_FS_TOTAL_FIFO_SIZE 1280 /* in Bytes */
4752
